		<title>17Social Concerns</title>
		<content> Pollution of food and environment by  
 the use of agro chemicals in modern   
 farm practice.                        
 Unemployment (farms all highly        
 mechanised and need fewer workers).   
 Lack of future prospects as there is  
 little industry.                      
 Social benefits for main income for   
 many families - proving inadequate in 
 many cases.                           
 The disasters in Third World countires
 cause concern, as does threat of      
 nuclear war.                          
 The continual erosion of public       
 services concerns many people.        
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       </content>
